Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyun Jun returns to the NSS after\Nhearing that Baek San and Jin Sa Woo,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who were being transported, had escaped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Sa Woo and Director Baek San\Nhave fled while being transported!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chul Young and Seon Hwa find\Na clue to yet another conspiracy,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.48,0:00:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and are coming to South Korea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go with you to South Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Jeong Hyung Jun is assassinated by Vick.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.83,0:00:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyun Jun finds Vick, but ends up\Nnot finding out anything about IRIS.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,0:00:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Baek San and Jin Sa Woo, where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyun Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.49,0:00:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The NSS captures Baek San in IRIS's hideout, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.97,0:00:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but Sa Woo and the mercenaries\Nhold a large number of people hostage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What? People are being held hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.12,0:01:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Final Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The assault team was trying to get\Nin and the booby trap got them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Check all the booby traps at all entrances\Nagain and strengthen our security.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.43,0:01:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We were caught by a booby trap\Nwhile attempting to enter the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.32,0:02:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't even confirmed the number of terrorists,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're trying to enter the building?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A counter-terrorist operation is all about moving out early.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know that we'll be at a disadvantage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,if we give the enemy time to\Nprepare against the assault?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't guarantee the safety of the hostages,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,then don't attempt an entry at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.98,0:02:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you to order me around?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- You want to die?\N- Go ahead and shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The assault team that was trying to\Nenter the building has been attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How many casualties?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Three people were killed because\Nthe bomb that was setup exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.21,0:02:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear the news on the scene directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please prepare the TP*
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}(*Tele Presence: a remote video conference system){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.85,0:02:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir, this is Kim Hyun Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, the operation will be directed by the NSS.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, the NSS will be directing the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll put the building entry on hold
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,until we have more information\Nabout the situation inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying we should let\Ngo of everything and wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the analysis from the NSS,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it can be inferred that the terrorists have a\Nbiochemical weapon in their possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A reckless entry may cause\Nthe death of all hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it was a situation where hostages were being held,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,where is the site of the operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go to the operation and return to the agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's in charge of the operation right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,TK1.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the site of the operation. Tell me the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you don't tell me, I can easily find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow me to go. I'm going\Nto go to the site of the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We're connected to the inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Aren't there any other ones?\N- It's just this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The fact that the only live circuit is\Naccurately showing the hostages,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,probably means that they're\Nshowing this to us on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Transmit the video capture from\Nthe security camera to the NSS,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so they can also see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, sir. I've captured the video\Nfrom the shopping mall's security camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll connect it so that it can also be viewed from that side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a live feed from a security\Ncamera inside the shopping mall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If we estimate the number of hostages\Nat a minimum... it's still past a hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And the terrorists are armed with automatic handguns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That gas mask you see around that guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a special gas mask for biochemical substances.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a model that surpasses normal\Ngas masks in filtering out chemicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they're going to use biochemical weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[Receiving call]\N[Foreign Affairs Minister Yu Kang Oh]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Park Chul Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll discuss it with those in Pyeong Yang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hostages are being held in the middle of Seoul.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They've captured the entirety of a giant mall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose doing is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Although the identity and the demands\Nof the terrorists aren't known yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,it's assumed that it has something to do with the summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.32,0:05:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's IRIS's doing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, is the VIP's schedule going to change?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's not confirmed yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Joong Bum, you check over the VIP's schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And Seon Hwa, you check to see how\Nthe hostage situation progresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've received orders from Section Chief\NPark to come support the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tae Sung is enough for giving\Nsupport in the operation here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to the agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If I stay at the agency,\NI'll be worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them about our demands as prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ready, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a video message that's just been transmitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think they're purposely feeding it to our equipment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Send it to the NSS as well.\N- I'm already sending it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,holding 107 hostages captive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All the entrances leading to the shopping mall
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.82,0:07:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,have been completely sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An explosive equipped with Soman gas{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}has been installed in the ventilation shafts of each entrance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,President Jo Myung Ho
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will announce what has been agreed\Nabout the summit tomorrow at 7:00 PM.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our demand is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that President Jo Myung Ho
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,announce the cancellation of the summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Also! We demand that he announces that\Nall economic ties with the North and South,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}talks between the North and South be cancelled,\Nand that the unified line between the North and South{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,be cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow at 7:00 PM,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,if the president does not make the\Nannouncements as we demanded,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the 107 here, along with thousands\Nof citizens around this shopping mall,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,will be sacrificed in the Soman gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is the penalty for attempting to break in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Under whose orders did you kill those hostages?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're from the NSS,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you must not know about the side that has to harm hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Terror literally means to deliver fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to acquire the demands we have set,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,clearly delivering fear is the secret to success.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My goal isn't unnecessary sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the way these guys and I work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,According to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the fear these guys will have towards me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,will dramatically increase if I kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go against my orders again,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean it's the work of IRIS again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Along with that, there was a demand to stop {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}all relations and talks with the North\Nand to announce that information.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They said if we don't announce it by that time, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they will use the biochemical weapons\Nthey have installed on the hostages.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that Soman gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In the G-series gases, there are\NTabun, Sarin, and Soman gases,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Soman gas is the nerve\Nagent with the highest death rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The gas will not only harm the\N107 people being held hostage,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but if it leaks out from the building,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it will harm people within a one kilometer radius.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Comrade Chief will enter South\NKorea tomorrow as scheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to take care of this situation\Nsomehow before the media conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an issue that puts the lives\Nof many hostages at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it will be taken care of that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't take care of the\Nsituation before the conference,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's no choice but to cancel the summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:12:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to investigate the scene also,\Nplease let us dispatch our men there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone from the North has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The director has given permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They failed to connect to the\Nshopping mall's security system,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,even from the NSS intelligence room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering the building's structure, there's\Nno way to deploy a spy camera into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If we risk the number of hostages,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,then we could disable the booby\Ntraps and enter the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't because of the Soman gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though they said it was with the hostages,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.94,0:12:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,considering the weak sustainability of the Soman gas,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a high chance that they\Ninstalled it in the ventilation room
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,or the air purifier to increase its efficiency.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's also too uncertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:13:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's important is that we\Nunderstand the situation inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the order?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to deliver our demands required for the next stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The NSS wants to send in an agent to negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I will directly deliver our demands this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyun Jun, it can't be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Send in someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really asking because you don't\Nknow? We're dealing with IRIS here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.97,0:13:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one in most danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're talking about danger,\Nit'll be the same for anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyun Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo will be inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm believing in,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,because Sa Woo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't the type of person to kill\Nduring negotiations at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn around and put your hands up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your hands down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.09,0:17:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I carefully thought about what you said,\Nhow I didn't know anything about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To see if it was really like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,To see if, during the short time we spent together,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,what it was that I knew about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- And what the memories we had shared togeth-\N- Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You've now sat down to negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- Just tell me if you're going to meet our demands or n-\N- Wait, Sa Woo, just listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When I thought about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.81,0:17:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I really did have a lot of things I\Ndidn't know about you, like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuff like being closer than blood brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is just another vague emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I really had a lot of things I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, when we went out to\NItaewon after finishing our 1000 li* march,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}(*li is a unit of measurement for distance;\N1 li = ~0.393 km; 1000 li = ~400 km){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:18:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get the tattoo with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,because the thought of tattooing a little bird
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and calling it a phoenix was so childish, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,if I think about it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why I didn't do it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've done...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to engrave our memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of being together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,have come too far
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring up such things as past memories now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I don't know anything about you at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know at least one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, you're making the wrong decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already done something\Nyou're going to regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you, Jin Sa Woo,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,hold those children hostage and threaten them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's definitely not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.26,0:19:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop blabbering on about useless things and\Ntell me the conditions for the negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.38,0:19:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say our side's demands first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Release the IRIS associates
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,who are being held in North Korea right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The terrorists have demanded something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They want us to release the IRIS members\Nwho are being held captive in North Korea,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and transport them to China and Syria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That is outside our authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's deliberately telling us to\Ntell the North to stop the summit,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and also meddle in their internal affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please call Park Chul Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I will deliver the message onto Comrade Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. I will contact you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than the cancellation of the North-\NSouth summit, there's another demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They're demanding that we release the IRIS\Nassociates who are being interrogated
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,by the security department, and transport them overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:21:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there a way to solve the problem\Nby using a plan to suppress them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The terrorists you are dealing with right\Nnow are not your average terrorists,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and Jin Sa Woo, who is leading them,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,was someone who was unsurpassed in the\Nspecial forces as a counter-terrorist specialist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Jin Sa Woo is involved in their plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.81,0:21:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,it will be difficult to have a rescue mission\Nthat involves no hostage casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a possibility that the hostages\Nwill be freed safely if I cancel the summit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.81,0:21:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to tell you honestly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no guarantee.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The president has given us permission\Nfor the counter-terrorist operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he willing to risk the lives of the hostages?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the decision of the NSS intelligence
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that they will not let the hostages go\Nsafely even if the demands are met.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, knowing that sacrificing hostages is inevitable,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,it's important that we keep that sacrifice to a minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.75,0:22:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We will meet all of your demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.98,0:22:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.94,0:22:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that we can reduce the number of unnecessary sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.57,0:22:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there is a condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.55,0:22:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.10,0:22:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the women and children go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I said we'll meet all of your demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:23:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not all of your hostages,\Njust the women and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.82,0:23:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.93,0:23:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Free the women and children right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.53,0:23:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.59,0:23:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,To kill all the hostages here,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.56,0:23:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is the order I received.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who ordered such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.50,0:24:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Bravo, enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.77,0:24:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.53,0:25:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You retard!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.50,0:25:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.73,0:25:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.13,0:25:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo. Sa Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.99,0:25:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.01,0:26:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo, Sa Woo, get a hold of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.08,0:26:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, man,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.46,0:26:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you've...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.55,0:26:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,made me...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.18,0:26:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,hell of a lot lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.64,0:26:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,H-h-hey, man,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.10,0:26:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,y-you...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.33,0:26:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,o-o-once...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.71,0:26:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know, I know, Sa Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.08,0:26:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I know your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.17,0:26:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to strain yourself to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.62,0:26:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say it. Don't do it. Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.23,0:26:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.65,0:27:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,never once...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.27,0:27:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,doubted your true feelings, Sa Woo...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.73,0:27:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,even till the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.64,0:27:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo. Sa Woo. Sa Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.28,0:27:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo. Sa Woo. Sa Woo, get a hold of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.32,0:27:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo, get a hold of yourself.\NGet a hold of yourself, Sa Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.81,0:27:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.96,0:27:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.69,0:27:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo. Sa Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.22,0:28:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sa Woo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.95,0:28:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sa Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.32,0:28:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You were never...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.09,0:28:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.21,0:28:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can never forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.10,0:28:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,S-s-s-s-sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.44,0:29:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,S-s-s-s-sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.17,0:29:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.55,0:29:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.84,0:29:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo. Sa Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.60,0:29:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.07,0:29:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.09,0:29:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.09,0:29:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo! Sa Woo!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.28,0:29:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.55,0:29:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.63,0:30:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know all your feelings. Sa Woo...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.23,0:30:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.85,0:30:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about Sa Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.91,0:30:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have brought him into the NSS...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.04,0:30:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.47,0:31:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fault is stopping me from killing Baek San.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.56,0:31:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand the fact that the\Nperson who killed all the people...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.27,0:31:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that have made a relationship with me, and made them suffer...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.19,0:31:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.39,0:31:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.18,0:31:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that living can give a worse pain than death.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.19,0:31:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They're looking for you in the Blue House.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.93,0:31:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Seung Hee.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.11,0:31:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.59,0:31:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're telling you to hurry up and\Nfinish up the operation, and report it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.15,0:31:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the director's order.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.26,0:31:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Go in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.13,0:32:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go in a little later.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.29,0:32:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.62,0:32:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I already said I won't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.83,0:32:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.41,0:32:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.49,0:32:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How have you been, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.23,0:32:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you've done well.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.89,0:32:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I wasn't able to prevent\Nthe sacrifices of a few citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.84,0:33:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,However, wasn't it due to that sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.70,0:33:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that we were able to show them that\Nthey aren't able to go against our will?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.26,0:33:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to leave after ten minutes if\Nyou want to meet the schedule you have
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.78,0:33:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,with the international press conference, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.80,0:33:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go first to see that the\Npreparations have been made.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.35,0:33:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.79,0:33:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rude, but may I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.73,0:33:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.91,0:33:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This summit,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.92,0:33:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is it worth so much that we have to go through with it
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.06,0:33:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,even with all these sacrifices?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.82,0:33:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, are you asking...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.12,0:33:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of value unification has right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.93,0:33:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In a historical advancement,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.92,0:33:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,pain is said to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.24,0:33:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If we avoid pain because we are afraid of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.26,0:33:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,then we won't be able to achieve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.20,0:34:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought your thoughts were the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.00,0:34:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.41,0:34:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,am not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.69,0:34:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The people who have been sacrificed in the past two years,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.34,0:34:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,have had nothing to do with summits, unification,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.79,0:34:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,or whatnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.07,0:34:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That historical advancement is worth it...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.88,0:34:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,for those who have been sacrificed,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.01,0:34:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.98,0:34:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is a day of our victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.91,0:34:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to let all our citizens know\Nthat we've gone past this ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.08,0:34:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you will be with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.05,0:34:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in the press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.79,0:35:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finished checking the surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.29,0:35:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no abnormalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.99,0:35:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no problems, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.27,0:35:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the team leader of the NSS's counter-terrorist department.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.49,0:35:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that security will be handled by both\Nthe presidential security and the NSS, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.05,0:35:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.89,0:35:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to check Code 1's route.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.45,0:35:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The space that's been prepared in front of the\Ninternational reporters section is the photo zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.87,0:35:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Code 1, after arriving along with the\NVIPs in area A, which is beside the road,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.14,0:36:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,will move here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.16,0:36:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,After taking photos with the international reporters,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.99,0:36:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Code 1 will move to the conference room.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.21,0:36:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.19,0:36:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Seung Hee]\N[Section Chief Park Sang Hyun]
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.18,0:36:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Calling]\N[Seung Hee]
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.49,0:36:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Section Chief. Where\Nare you right now, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.85,0:36:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to the agency with\Nthe bodies of the terrorists
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.86,0:36:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that we've collected, along with their possessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.64,0:36:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.42,0:37:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the press conference escorting Code 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.77,0:37:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Section Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.18,0:37:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they find team leader Choi\NSeung Hee's whereabouts?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.75,0:37:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Choi Seung Hee?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.55,0:37:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.00,0:37:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she came back to the\Nagency, but she's not here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.66,0:37:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She reported in just a minute ago from the security car.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.84,0:37:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She's at the press conference right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.32,0:37:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The press conference?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.03,0:37:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard her, right? She's\Nat the press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.55,0:37:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I heard. All right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.14,0:37:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Section Chief Park! Section Chief Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.39,0:37:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Section Chief Park!\NSection Chief Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.18,0:37:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Section Chief Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.80,0:37:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're out of breath.\NIs something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.98,0:37:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We killed the wrong people.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.13,0:37:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.49,0:37:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The dead terrorists, weren't terrorists at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.56,0:37:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The results from the body identification unit came back,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.36,0:37:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and the people we thought were terrorists,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.83,0:37:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,were actually the hostages\Nbeing held in the shopping mall.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.09,0:37:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The bastards disguised the\Nhostages as the terrorists!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.75,0:37:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.53,0:38:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.61,0:38:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.51,0:38:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the reporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.97,0:38:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Number 3, at destination.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.22,0:38:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Receiving call]\N[Section Chief Park Sang Hyun]
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.22,0:38:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.08,0:39:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- We're in big trouble.\N- What's the matter, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.95,0:39:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All the terrorists at the scene are free now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.64,0:39:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The people we killed weren't the terrorists,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.77,0:39:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but hostages that were disguised as terrorists!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.63,0:39:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure if they have something else in mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.99,0:39:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They will arrive soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.01,0:39:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Code 1, one minute until arrival.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.63,0:39:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Checking location.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.02,0:39:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sierra 1, check.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.52,0:39:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sierra 2, check.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.27,0:39:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sierra 3, check.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.95,0:39:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.39,0:39:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We've acquired the sniper locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.89,0:39:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,First team, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.47,0:39:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of you, be on standby here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.24,0:40:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The VIP will arrive first, then Code 1 will arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.01,0:41:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the weather is very cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.09,0:43:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.33,0:43:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.18,0:43:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hyun Jun]
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.19,0:43:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hyun Jun]
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.08,0:44:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take the president and go.\N- Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.60,0:44:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we have to move, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.99,0:44:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and move!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.45,0:46:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Seon Hwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.93,0:46:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.08,0:46:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.33,0:46:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Seon Hwa get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.66,0:46:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.71,0:46:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.26,0:46:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.03,0:46:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.51,0:46:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.91,0:46:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.95,0:46:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.02,0:47:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the ideals I embrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.69,0:47:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They were too big for a vessel* like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.69,0:47:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}(*Korean idiom meaning a person's capability.){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.25,0:47:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,For a larger, more sufficient vessel to take its place,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.39,0:47:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to break the small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.13,0:48:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.27,0:48:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't a bundle of flowers and\Nsaying thanks a little lacking,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.10,0:48:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,when the Republic's greatest\Nwarrior saved your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.58,0:48:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I kept thinking about it on the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.60,0:48:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but nothing would come to mind, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.00,0:49:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave, so think about something good to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.26,0:49:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.49,0:49:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,just these flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.74,0:49:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.82,0:50:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to Pyeong Yang tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.91,0:50:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be coming back down along with Our Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.41,0:50:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What would I be doing by then?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.16,0:50:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's for sure is that I won't be by the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.09,0:50:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,because I don't want to be involved\Nin such a horrible incident again.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.15,0:50:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know when I'll be coming back,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.03,0:50:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but I hope there won't be a situation\Nwhere we have to point guns at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.52,0:50:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.74,0:51:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That time,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.50,0:51:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,at the moment the president\Nappeared at the press conference...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.04,0:51:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.73,0:51:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The debt you have in your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.90,0:51:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it isn't easy for you to get rid of it all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.72,0:51:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.30,0:51:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you prayed for me not to have\Nnightmares when I was asleep, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.24,0:51:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll be the one to do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.87,0:51:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you can quickly get away...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.45,0:51:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,from your dark past.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.42,0:51:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}There's a wind is blowing inside my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.47,0:52:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}Your image is being erased{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.51,0:52:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}While having a dream called regret,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.32,0:52:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Three months later]
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.54,0:52:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}I stand here here missing you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.55,0:52:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}I lasted a day because {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.45,0:52:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}you said you love me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.70,0:52:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}I lasted a month because{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.55,0:52:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Section Chief Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.14,0:52:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Section Chief Hwang was here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.97,0:52:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all go out to eat today. It's all on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.77,0:52:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why are you doing that all of a sudden?\N- Did something good happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.50,0:52:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They went up. Five consecutive\Ntimes! Everything that I bought!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.56,0:52:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.83,0:52:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've ever had something like this in the\Nthirty-two years of my investments!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.38,0:52:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Bravo! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.59,0:52:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,By any chance, you're not planning anything, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.06,0:52:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mrs. Hwang,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.28,0:52:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just kidding, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.67,0:52:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Which type of stock was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.40,0:52:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to care about\Ntypes of stocks nowadays,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.19,0:52:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,everything I touch turns to gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.55,0:52:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, the North-South summit is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.71,0:53:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you suppressed all of the evil crimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.04,0:53:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to go all out for sure today!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.33,0:53:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to call Hyun Jun and Seung Hee.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.33,0:53:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to look for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.75,0:53:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't ever be coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.50,0:53:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.74,0:53:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just going to keep on sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.31,0:53:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.04,0:53:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.14,0:53:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then order something from room service for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.02,0:53:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to be like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.46,0:53:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Get washed and come out immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.00,0:54:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, were you always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.64,0:54:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.87,0:54:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, did you always nag me so much before?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.96,0:54:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't even count as nagging you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.57,0:54:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my god...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.13,0:54:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? Quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.68,0:54:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.23,0:54:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.62,0:54:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.14,0:54:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get up!\N- All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.48,0:54:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.14,0:54:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.51,0:54:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, single-celled organism!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.90,0:54:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a single celled organism, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.23,0:54:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You whine when you're hungry and\Ngo all happy when I feed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.04,0:54:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you're any different?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.92,0:54:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.50,0:54:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yesterday, you didn't even let me sleep...\N- Hey! What, when did I, do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.48,0:54:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.65,0:54:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}You cannot hear me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.71,0:55:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}If we had met and loved{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.78,0:55:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}during different times,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.73,0:55:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}a different place,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.41,0:55:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}would we be happy right now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.64,0:55:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}For the rest of my life,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.28,0:55:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}It should have been you, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.42,0:55:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}But, now it will only be my staggering figure...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.88,0:55:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}Since I can't hate you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.97,0:55:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}or forget you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.07,0:55:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They're really cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.28,0:55:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They're pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.93,0:55:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, should we have five?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.27,0:55:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- Our kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.49,0:55:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you have big dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.94,0:55:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What, are you proposing to me right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.13,0:55:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you could look at it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.68,0:55:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give me five of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.46,0:56:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of a proposal is\Nhaphazard and without a ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.26,0:56:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my god, I can't recognize this at all. I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.86,0:56:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Why are you so picky?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.65,0:56:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.13,0:56:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}For the rest of my life,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.74,0:56:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}It should have been you, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.90,0:56:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}But now it will only be my staggering figure...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.38,0:56:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}Since I can't hate you{\i0}
